news.title: Delhi HC quashes DDA demolition notice for encroachment removal in Mehrauli
news.para: A bench headed by Chief Justice Satish Chandra Sharma said regardless of the environmental imperatives or earlier court orders, the DDA's obligation to act as per law and ensure procedural fairness to those affected by its actions remains intact.

news.title: NBCC (India)'s net profit declines 16.19% in Q2 FY24
news.para: NBCC (India)'s net consolidated total income stood at Rs 2,129.09 crore in Q2 FY24, a growth of 2.66 per cent from Rs 2,073.89 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Orient Cement posts net profit of Rs 24.62 crore in Q2 FY24
news.para: Orient Cement's net consolidated total income stood at Rs 722.24 crore in Q2 FY24, a growth of 16.47 per cent from Rs 620.11 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.
